     <div type="to_the_reader">
   <pb facs="4"/>
   <head>Ad Lectorem Hexasticon.</head>
   <l>In lucem prodit tenebris exuta malignis</l>
   <l>Romulei petulās, vaesana{que} flammula Phoebi:</l>
   <l>Rorātem Authori (Lectores) spargite florē,</l>
   <l>Intyba, Narcissos, Latacen, picti{que} roseti</l>
   <l>Dulces diuitias: Illum concingite lauru:</l>
   <l>Emerito solers industria reddat honorem.</l>
   <closer>
      <signed>Thomas Watson. <hi>Oxon.</hi>
      </signed>
   </closer>
</div>
